xdg-utils: xdg-utils (Freedesktop Integration Scripts)
xdg-utils:
xdg-utils: Xdg-utils is a set of command line tools that assist applications 
xdg-utils: with a variety of desktop integration tasks, and includes scripts to 
xdg-utils: install desktop menus, icons, query file type handling, open a file
xdg-utils: or url, send mail, and control the screensaver.
